com.google.code.objectprops
Class Formatter

java.lang.Object
  com.google.code.objectprops.Formatter
Direct Known Subclasses:
DefaultFormatter
public class Formatter
extends java.lang.Object

The Formatter can convert a Java object to a String representation and vice versa. It can be extended to format a specific type by adding an appropriate instance of IFormat.

Author:
Michael Karneim
